Class StackList<T>

  • java.lang.Object

  • Type Parameters:

    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>

    public class StackList<T>
extends LinkedList<T>
implements java.lang.Iterable<T>
    Objects of type StackList manage items in a singly linked list. Have two inner classes, Node class and StackIterator class for iterating on Objects of type StackList.

    swati
